,"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"borders","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract31AllBorderSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/borders","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of border semantic tokens to use for button borders"}],"title":"borders","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"OUDSRadioButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckboItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/allbordersemantictokensprovider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of border"}],"title":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]}}}